dge Walker is scheduled to hear Apple's motion on March23.andM;The motion was tinged with a certain acerbity: &quot;Xerox should be left where ithas placed itself for the past decade, observing the work of others from thesidelines,&quot; it stated.andP;  n</TEXT></DOC>